column8: The Ashanti is a great looking tee made from high-quality, durable material. We have put this shirt through a battery of tests and it has stood up well: no shrinking, staining or fading. Straight hem. Durable double-needle stitching. Tagless printed label for added comfort. 6 oz. jersey-knit fabric. Imported. Machine wash and dry.
